reviewText: This series is awesome!  I could watch it over and over.  The lessons in this series are thought provoking and practical, and if we apply the things that are taught, it will be life-changing.
TD Jakes, Always brings the word in a touching way.. you can get a lot from his teachings, one of the most powerful preachers HANDS DOWN!!

THIS BOX INCLUDES

STILL FRIENDS
LIVING WITH RESTRICTIONS
IT WILL ALL COME OUT IN THE FIRE

I ENJOYED THESE DVDS AS ALWAYS JAKES PREACHED. WELL RECOMMENDED AND HOPE YOU
ENJOY.LIVING WITH RESTRICTIONS TALKS ABOUT THINGS GOD DELIVERED US FROM AND HOW WE LIVE OUR NEW CHRISTIAN LIVES BUT WE MUST NOT GO BACK TO WHAT GOD DELIVERED US FROM. IT WILL ALL COME OUT IN THE FIRE SPEAKS OF GOING THROUGH THE FIRE AND WHATEVER PROBLEMS HABBITS OR WHATEVER YOUR BATTLE IS WILL COME OUT IN THE FIRE PEOPLE THAT ARE REALLY NOT YOUR FRIENDS WILL BE REVEALED IN THE FIRE A VERY BLESSED AND ANOINTED MESSAGE.
